p-values interpretation

Source: R/interpret_p.R
interpret_p.Rd

p-values interpretation

interpret_p(p, rules = "default")

Arguments

p

Value or vector of p-values.
rules

Can be "default" or custom set of rules().

Examples

interpret_p(.02)
#> [1] "significant"
interpret_p(c(.5, .02))
#> [1] "not significant" "significant"
